### 获取 JWT Token（假设有 /api/login）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 提交单份报告（需替换 {{token}}）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "avg": "4.8",
  "high": "结构清晰、目标明确",
  "low": "表达模糊",
  "advice": "添加上下文说明;引导 AI 举例说明",
  "comments": ["很有帮助", "建议增加案例"]
}

### 批量上传报告
POST http://localhost:3000/api/report/batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  { "avg": "4.5", "high": "表达准确", "low": "缺乏互动", "advice": "增加互动", "comments": ["内容具体"] },
  { "avg": "3.9", "high": "结构清晰", "low": "缺乏上下文", "advice": "补充背景", "comments": ["希望有更多说明"] }
]

### 查询所有报告
GET http://localhost:3000/api/report
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
